==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀναπολόγητος / anapologētos / an-ap-ol-og'-ay-tos
*From G1 (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of G626; indefensible: 

===Adjective===
'''ἀναπολόγητος'''

# without excuse, [[inexcuseable]].

